properties.SQL Query:
SELECT instrument_key  as security_id
                FROM v_upstox_options 
                WHERE name = 'NIFTY' AND option_type='CE'
                AND strike::numeric = (( SELECT floor((vsi.ltp + 0::numeric) / 100::numeric) * 100::numeric
                       FROM ( SELECT upstox_live_index.ltp
                               FROM upstox_live_index
                              WHERE upstox_live_index.instrument_key = 'NSE_INDEX|Nifty 50'::text
                              ORDER BY upstox_live_index.ltt DESC
                             LIMIT 1) vsi));
SELECT count(*) as count FROM upstox_orders_api WHERE position_status = 'Open' and put_call ='${option_type}';
SELECT count(*) as count FROM upstox_orders_api WHERE position_status = 'Open' and put_call ='${option_type}';

SELECT instrument_key  as security_id
                FROM v_upstox_options
                WHERE name = 'NIFTY' AND option_type='PE'
                AND strike::numeric = (( SELECT ceil((vsi.ltp + 0::numeric) / 100::numeric) * 100::numeric
                       FROM ( SELECT upstox_live_index.ltp
                               FROM upstox_live_index
                              WHERE upstox_live_index.instrument_key = 'NSE_INDEX|Nifty 50'::text
                              ORDER BY upstox_live_index.ltt DESC
                             LIMIT 1) vsi));
